<p data-pp-blocktype="copy" data-pp-id="2.0">Returning to his home state of Utah, where more babies are born with cleft lip and palate than is typical, Dr. Devan Griner made plans to open his own practice, joining the small cohort of plastic surgeons nationwide who treat the condition.</p>
        
    
                        


   
            
