    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/after-walmart-bought-finance-app-one-complaints-soared">
                                    Walmart Bought a Finance App and Reduced Fraud Protections. Guess What Happened Next?
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            The retail giant has long sought to become a financial powerhouse. But after it acquired a neobank called One in 2022, fraud complaints multiplied and customer reviews cratered.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/craig-silverman">Craig Silverman</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/peter-elkind">Peter Elkind</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-03-11EDT05:00">March 11, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
