        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/railroad-safety-data-missing-dead-workers-severed-limbs">
                                    What’s Missing From Railroad Safety Data? Dead Workers and Severed Limbs.
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Thanks to government loopholes, rail companies haven’t been scrutinized by the Federal Railroad Administration for scores of alleged worker injuries and at least two deaths.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/topher-sanders">Topher Sanders</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/dan-schwartz">Dan Schwartz</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/danelle-morton">Danelle Morton</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/gabriel-sandoval">Gabriel Sandoval</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-03-13EDT05:00">March 13, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
